{"tid":727723,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"清魚缸底發現呢粒野，有無養魚嘅巴絲幫手睇下","createTime":"2018-07-03T08:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T08:34:28.000Z","uid":1852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"959c6012e47fad63e28460903ac3fddd3086216d","tid":727723,"uid":1852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/160239_60002a0fe50d43a0b8e624bfd40e6236.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F160239_60002a0fe50d43a0b8e624bfd40e6236.png&h=c88ebe83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近公司老闆買左缸魚仔返黎，放左三日假返黎生晒青苔，水底d 草又死晒，剛剛吸吸下缸底d 污糟野發現上圖果粒野，想問係咪卵黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD魚仔就係下圖呢d,我都唔知係乜名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/160600_a277982eb37cdc67dc070f8b21ec802e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F160600_a277982eb37cdc67dc070f8b21ec802e.png&h=98b43b69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果係產左卵，我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全未養過魚唔知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aadcaccbde875b55071dd11e41c78100134d2dd","tid":727723,"uid":1852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1e62112dc1fba25dd8e03ba377364c4c1538c9","tid":727723,"uid":111644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:34:54.000Z","msg":"應該係螺既蛋"},{"pid":"97d8516e156db63166e1b669cb13a1021678146f","tid":727723,"uid":175820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:37:53.000Z","msg":"好似係鯉魚王黎"},{"pid":"abac4a8e6c38c79a4e027bd383d9b0ea9b8b6d5b","tid":727723,"uid":52796